CREATE EXTERNAL TABLE [dbo].[ext_FACT_PURCHLINE] WITH (
        LOCATION = 'FACT_PURCHLINE/Archive',
        DATA_SOURCE = [eds_tx-halfen-2-dwh],
        FILE_FORMAT = [eff_Parquet]
) AS
SELECT
    *
FROM
    OPENROWSET(
        BULK './FACT_PURCHLIN/In/2023/01/05/FACT_PURCHLINE_2023_01_05_04_54_43_296.parquet',
        FORMAT = 'PARQUET'
    ) AS [result]
WHERE DATAAREAID NOT IN (5307, 5309, 5310, 5325)
